==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cremate
<hw>Cre"mate</hw> <pr>(kr?"m?t ⟦or⟧ kr?-m?t")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>crematus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>cremare</ets> to burn; cf.
Skr. <ets>cr<?/</ets> to cook.]</ety> <def>To burn; to reduce to ashes
by the action of fire, either directly or in an oven or retort; to
incremate or incinerate; <as>as, to <ex>cremate</ex> a corpse, instead
of burying it</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cremation</ent>⟦br⟧
